{"word":"H748 - אָרַךְ - ʼârak - aw-rak' - Defer","slug":"H748","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָרַךְ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼârak"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-rak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Defer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E8;&#x05DA; - 'a&#x0302;rak</b> - <i>aw-rak'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>long</i> (literally or figuratively): - defer, draw out, lengthen, (be, become, make, pro-) long, + (out-, over-) live, tarry (long)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H724\">H724</a>, <a href=\"#/H750\">H750</a>, <a href=\"#/H751\">H751</a>, <a href=\"#/H752\">H752</a>, <a href=\"#/H753\">H753</a>, <a href=\"#/H757\">H757</a>"}]}